! Case I
`Listwidger` without variable. See how `!!filed` works. They refer to the each tiddler results from list widget.

```
<$list filter="[tag[exmp03]]" variable="myTid">
Title: {{!!title}}<br>
This is the variable `myTid`: <<myTid>><br>
Test-Filed: {{!!test-field}}<br>
</$list>
```
<$list filter="[tag[exmp03]]" variable="myTid">
